General.Name: Paos Holdings Bhd
General.Description: Paos Holdings Berhad, an investment holding company, manufactures and deals in soaps and its related products in Malaysia, South East Asia, and internationally. It operates through three segments: Manufacturing, Trading, and Integrated Hotel Operations and Property Investment. The company is involved in the contract manufacturing of bar soaps and animal feeds; and toll manufacturing of products from palm oil and specialty fats. It also trades in specialty fats produce from palm oil, as well as marine gas oil. In addition, the company operates and manages hotels and restaurants; invests in properties; and owns and rents retail podium and office space. It also exports its products to Japan, Indonesia, Thailand, and the Philippines. Paos Holdings Berhad was incorporated in 1997 and is headquartered in Shah Alam, Malaysia.
